title: Adam Natkho
text:
Adam Cherimovich Natkho (, ; born 14 February 1959) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and former player.
Personal life.
Adam is a <a href="Adyghe%20people">Circassian</a> by nationality. He is related to <a href="Bibras%20Natkho">Bibras Natkho</a> and is the father of <a href="Amir%20Natkho">Amir Natkho</a>.
